    </item>
    <item>
      <title>关税和就业担忧导致消费者信心下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-24/consumer-sentiment-drops-on-tariff-employment-concerns-video</link>
      <description><![CDATA[密歇根大学称，1 月份最终信心指数从 12 月份的 74 降至三个月以来的最低点 71.1。消费者预计未来五到十年内价格将以年率 3.2% 上涨，高于 12 月份预期的 3%。Mike McKee 报道了“彭博未平仓合约”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/videos/2025-01-24/consumer-sentiment-drops-on-tariff-employment-concerns-video</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 24 Jan 2025 15:51:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
